Lorraine Vélez https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lorraine_V%C3%A9lez 0 Lorraine Vélez (born November 2, 1964) is an American singer and actress of Puerto Rican descent, who has specialized in musical theatre. Her name has sometimes appeared as Loraine Velez. She is the twin sister of actress Lauren Vélez.
